人拒掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"屌師兄幾時去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋試下一個簽領事館一個網上簽"},{"pid":"5a7e3cf0ab79779c5ddcea5c6dc7ebbb8033f0eb","tid":759441,"uid":54880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄我又係諗住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都未搞簽證，不過聽講好多網上簽證都ok過到，但有冇咩網推介</blockquote><br />\n你google下電子簽證 都係果個網搞<br />\n過唔過到我都想知先上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9893826f2deb5667297742b77b7de786a27a83a","tid":759441,"uid":54880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁我網上搞算啦 真係平好多<br />\n應該唔會咁撚柒被人拒掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>屌師兄幾時去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋試下一個簽領事館一個網上簽</blockquote><br />\n你唔係想d價錢加埋除返2呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊網上搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a587cd28682d62505d964a1fbc683f55eb18747d","tid":759441,"uid":96501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e25bbac702abad36c00032dd8e57f25783c77163","tid":759441,"uid":54880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"連一開波個簽證都唔知點 上網睇話搞完簽證到時都未必100%入到境 你地有冇人試過電子簽證個隻?係咪都有機會比人拒入境<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果去4日3夜 你地推薦去邊好?北越定南越?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"淨係今年都去過越南六次（3次去胡志明，1次峴港，1次河內，1次大叻），<br />\n次次都係上網整完Print出來，去到整落地簽證，<br />\n無一次失敗。"},{"pid":"b88623a7ddaf8503c09098435089e041c97c729f","tid":759441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a587cd28682d62505d964a1fbc683f55eb18747d","tid":759441,"uid":96501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e25bbac702abad36c00032dd8e57f25783c77163","tid":759441,"uid":54880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"連一開波個簽證都唔知點 上網睇話搞完簽證到時都未必100%入到境 你地有冇人試過電子簽證個隻?係咪都有機會比人拒入境<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果去4日3夜 你地推薦去邊好?北越定南越?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"淨係今年都去過越南六次（3次去胡志明，1次峴港，1次河內，1次大叻），<br />\n次次都係上網整完Print出來，去到整落地簽證，<br />\n無一次失敗。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"你上網見到佢有好多隻簽證，香港人最常用就係單次簽證同埋三個月多次簽證，分別就顧名思義啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單次：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/003229_aebe8443be4976f1c964b7fbbeac82f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F003229_aebe8443be4976f1c964b7fbbeac82f5.png&h=28b5fe26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多次：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/003339_e6caa11bd8951e82ae59289dfd91971d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F003339_e6caa11bd8951e82ae59289dfd91971d.png&h=a3c2d051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你上網求其搵一間都可以，填完個人資料之後就俾錢，比完錢兩三日後你就會收到email，入邊應該會有一份兩至三頁嘅嘢，應該除咗你個名之外會見到好多你唔識嘅人嘅名，Print出黎帶去。<br />\n<br />\n另外，佢應該會叫你填埋份Form，咁你落機去到機場，會見到個visa counter（好顯眼，唔會搵唔到），比哂呢啲嘢佢（連同一幅相），佢會暫時拎起咗你本Passport，你就等嗌名就得。<br />\n<br />\n跟手拎返本Passport之後，你會發現佢哋係你本Passport入邊貼左一張貼紙，然後你就可以過海關。<br />\n<br />\n好容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3235e13140d60f1ff546b40c8ce05cb79497febc","tid":759441,"uid":23458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88623a7ddaf8503c09098435089e041c97c729f","tid":759441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a587cd28682d62505d964a1fbc683f55eb18747d","tid":759441,"uid":96501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e25bbac702abad36c00032dd8e57f25783c77163","tid":759441,"uid":54880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"